| dead-url = yes
}}</ref>和[[亞太|亞太]]區第二繁忙的客運航線。<ref>{{cite press release
 |title       = OAG reveals latest industry intelligence on the busiest routes
 |publisher   = [[OAG|OAG]]
 |date        = 2007-09-21
 |url         = http://www.oag.com/oag/website/com/en/PopUps/Print/Press+Releases/OAG+reveals+latest+industry+intelligence+on+the+busiest+routes+2109072
 |accessdate  = 2008-08-23
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20101113060709/http://www.oag.com/oag/website/com/en/PopUps/Print/Press%2BReleases/OAG%2Breveals%2Blatest%2Bindustry%2Bintelligence%2Bon%2Bthe%2Bbusiest%2Broutes%2B2109072
 |archivedate = 2010-11-13
}}</ref>墨爾本機場擁有多條直航航線前往澳洲所有首府、各[[大洋洲|大洋洲]]、[[亞洲|亞洲]]、[[非洲|非洲]]、[[歐洲|歐洲]]、[[北美洲|北美洲]]及[[南美洲|南美洲]]航點。墨爾本機場是[[澳洲航空|澳洲航空]]、[[維珍藍航空|維珍藍航空]]、[[欣豐虎航|欣豐虎航]]的[[樞紐機場|樞紐機場]]。至2008年12月開始，墨爾本機場的出口貨運量列澳洲各機場之冠；進口貨運量則列澳洲第二。<ref>{{cite press release
| title = Melbourne air freight exports top Sydney for the first time
| publisher = [[Victorian_Government|Victorian Government]]
| date = 2009-02-26
| url = http://www.premier.vic.gov.au/minister-for-industry-trade/melbourne-air-freight-exports-top-sydney-for-first-time.html
| accessdate = 2009-03-04
}}{{Dead link}}</ref>兩家貨運航空公司{{lang|en|Australian air Express}}和{{lang|en|Toll Priority}}的總部均設於墨爾本機場；機場的國內貨物吞吐量亦列全澳之冠。<ref>{{cite web
