}}</ref>墨爾本機場被{{lang|en|[[Skytrax|Skytrax]]}}評為四星級機場。<ref name=skytrax>{{cite web
| title = World Airport Star Ranking
| publisher = [[Skytrax|Skytrax]]
| url = http://www.airlinequality.com/AirportRanking/ranking-A-Z.htm
| accessdate = 2008-08-12
| archive-date = 2013-07-14
| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6I5xZ9cww?url=http://www.airlinequality.com/AirportRanking/ranking-A-Z.htm
| dead-url = no
}}</ref> 墨爾本機場有四座航廈，澳洲航空及其附屬公司[[捷星航空|捷星航空]]使用第一航廈；第二航廈供國際航班停泊；第三航廈供維珍藍色航空使用第四航廈將供廉價航空澳洲虎航使用，四座航廈共有56個登機閘口。機場在2012年拆除曾經擁有的舊第四航廈，在此基礎興建一座新的大容量航廈；而第一航廈則與第二航廈共同提供國際航廈業務，並且新增兩條新跑道。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.smh.com.au/travel/travel-news/melbourne-airport-poised-to-spread-its-wings-20111207-1oj6z.html |title=Melbourne Airport poised to spread its wings |access-date=2012-02-23 |archive-date=2012-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210084423/http://www.smh.com.au/travel/travel-news/melbourne-airport-poised-to-spread-its-wings-20111207-1oj6z.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 機場運作 ==

=== 航線發展 ===
2005至2007年，墨爾本機場的國際旅客流量下跌50萬人次。<ref name=tullableeds>{{cite news
| last = Moynihan
| first = Stephen
| title = Tiger bites into fares, but Tulla bleeds
| publisher = [[The_Age|The Age]]
| date = 2007-07-13
| url = http://www.theage.com.au/news/national/tiger-bites-into-fares-but-tulla-bleeds/2007/07/12/1183833691213.html
| accessdate = 2008-07-31
| archive-date = 2012-11-05
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121105153245/http://www.theage.com.au/news/national/tiger-bites-into-fares-but-tulla-bleeds/2007/07/12/1183833691213.html
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>雖然墨爾本機場的乘客量屢創新高，但2006年的統計顯而航空公司正在減少航班。[[英國航空|英國航空]]撤出墨爾本後，[[澳洲航空|澳洲航空]]在2006年3月增加往倫敦的航班以彌補流失的客量。<ref>{{cite news
| title = Qantas to double flights between Melbourne and London
| publisher = Asia Travel Tips
| date = 2005-12-15
| url = http://www.asiatraveltips.com/news05/1512-London.shtml
| accessdate = 2008-07-31
| archive-date = 2019-06-04
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190604192546/http://www.asiatraveltips.com/news05/1512-London.shtml
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>2006年第四季機場的國際旅客數字跌了2%，<ref> {{cite web |url=http://www.melair.com.au/about_airport/media_releases_item.asp?id=276 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-12-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070311055220/http://www.melair.com.au/about_airport/media_releases_item.asp?id=276 |archivedate=2007-03-11 }} Record passenger numbers for Melbourne Airport] 2005</ref>而機場最後一家歐洲航空公司－[[奧地利航空|奧地利航空]]亦於2007年3月撤出。<ref>{{cite news
| last = Moynihan
| first = Stephen
