==  交通配套 ==
=== 汽車 ===
[[File:Tullamarine_fwy.jpg|right]]
墨爾本機場由Tullamarine Freeway經過收費高速公司CityLink連接，直達距離23公里（14英里）的商業中心區，機場附近設有兩個分別通往機場客運大樓和空運貨站的公路入口。<ref name=offramp>{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/about_airport/media_releases_item.asp?id=311
 |title       = Second Airport entry road opens
 |work        = Melbourne Airport Media Releases
 |publisher   = Melbourne Airport
 |accessdate  = 2008-09-27
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20080722001959/http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/about_airport/media_releases_item.asp?id=311
 |archivedate = 2008-07-22
}}</ref>機場設有5座24小時運作的收費停車場。多層室內停車場提供短期及商用停車位；露天停車場亦提供長期停車位。<ref>{{cite web
 |title       = Melbourne Airport — Parking
 |publisher   = Melbourne Airport
 |url         = http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/to_from_airport/parking/
 |accessdate  = 2008-06-30
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20080512054552/http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/to_from_airport/parking/
 |archivedate = 2008-05-12
}}</ref>現時的多層停車場由1999年起多次擴建而成，以取代原有的地面停車場。<ref name=report1999>{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/downloads/pdfs/APACAnnualReport1999.pdf
 |format      = PDF
 |title       = 1999 Annual Report
 |publisher   = [[Australia_Pacific_Airports_Corporation_Limited|Australia Pacific Airports Corporation Limited]]
 |accessdate  = 2008-07-29
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20080724033809/http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/downloads/pdfs/APACAnnualReport1999.pdf
 |archivedate = 2008-07-24
}}</ref>

[[File:Skybus_Super_Shuttle.jpg|thumb]]

=== 公共交通 ===
機場巴士（Skybus）是前往機場的主要交通工具，旅客由機場前往墨爾本商業中心區的[[南十字車站|南十字車站]]約需22分鐘。2017年8月时票价为成人19澳元。<ref name=bus>{{cite web
 |url        = http://www.metlinkmelbourne.com.au/timetables/airport_buses
 |title        = Airport buses — Metlink — Your guide to public transport in Melbourne and Victoria
 |publisher        = www.metlinkmelbourne.com.au
 |accessdate        = 2008-07-29
 |archive-date        = 2012-03-29
 |archive-url        = https://www.webcitation.org/66X8ic4zn?url=http://www.metlinkmelbourne.com.au/timetables/airport-buses
 |dead-url        = yes
 }}</ref>除了機場巴士，還有3條沿用Myki收費系統的巴士線前往机场西站马修大街，乘客可在此换乘59路电车前往城区，分別為478線、479線及482線。479路另一端的终点为桑伯里站，乘客可在此换乘v-line前往本迪戈，伊丘卡和天鹅岭。<ref name=bus/>
2010年年底起，SmartBus開辨墨爾本機場至法蘭克斯頓的巴士路線，沿途經Gladstone Park、Roxburgh Park、布莱德明都（Broadmeadows）、艾平（Epping）、Greensborough、唐卡斯特（Doncaster）、布力般（Blackburn）、靈伍德（Ringwood）及丹德農（Dandenong）。

其他9家巴士公司提供前往[[柏拉瑞特|柏拉瑞特]]、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.airportshuttlebus.com.au/ |title=Ballaret Airport Shuttle website |access-date=2009-10-19 |archive-date=2021-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221231342/https://airportshuttlebus.com.au/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[本迪戈_(維多利亞州)|本迪戈]]、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bendigoairportservice.com.au/ |title=Bendigo Airport Service website |access-date=2009-10-19 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124154301/https://bendigoairportservice.com.au/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 丹德農、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.airportbusdandenong.com.au/ |title=Airport Bus Dandenong website |access-date=2009-10-19 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226133815/https://www.airportbusdandenong.com.au/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[弗蘭克斯頓|法蘭克斯頓]]、[[莫寧頓半島|摩寧頓半島]]、<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fapas.com.au/ |title=Frankston & Penninsula Bus Service website |access-date=2009-10-19 |archive-date=2016-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160620174113/http://www.fapas.com.au/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[吉朗_(維多利亞州)|基隆]]、[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]近郊、雪帕頓（Shepparton） 和[[里弗里納|里弗里納]]的巴士服務。<ref>{{cite web
 |title       = Melbourne Airport — Bus Services
 |publisher   = Melbourne Airport
 |url         = http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/to_from_airport/bus_services.asp
 |accessdate  = 2008-07-29
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20090204042602/http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/to_from_airport/bus_services.asp
 |archivedate = 2009-02-04
}}</ref>旅客無須轉乘V/Line列車前往以上各城鎮。Airport Direct每天開出一班來回[[維多利亞州|維多利亞州]]北部雪帕頓、Nagambie、西摩（Seymour）和Broadford的長途客車服務。<ref>{{cite web
 |title       = Airport Direct — Timetable
 |publisher   = Airport Direct
 |url         = http://www.airportdirect.com.au/timetable.shtml
 |accessdate  = 2008-07-29
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20080720224257/http://www.airportdirect.com.au/timetable.shtml
 |archivedate = 2008-07-20
}}</ref> Bendigo Airport Service每天開出四班來往本迪戈至機場時客車。Gull Bus每一至兩小時開出一班前往-{zh-hans:吉朗;zh-hant:基隆}-的客車。<ref>{{cite web
| title = Gull Bus Services — Timetable
