=== 其他設施 ===
[[Image:Hilton_Melbourne_Airport.jpg|250px]]]]

墨爾本機場附近設有4間酒店。提供280間房間的[[希爾頓酒店|希爾頓酒店]]坐落於第二航廈100米外的多層停車場上蓋，於2000年年中落成。<ref name=report1999/>假日酒店（{{lang|en|Holiday Inn}}）、{{lang|en|Motel Formule 1}}及{{lang|en|Mantra Tullamarine}}則距離主航廈範圍600米至2公里不等。<ref>{{cite web
 |title       = Melbourne Airport — Hotels
 |publisher   = Melbourne Airport
 |url         = http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/airport_facilities/hotels.asp
 |accessdate  = 2008-09-27
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20081204110029/http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/airport_facilities/hotels.asp
 |archivedate = 2008-12-04
}}</ref> 機場的入口設有一間[[BP|BP]]加油站、[[平治|平治]]汽車代理和一間[[麥當勞|麥當勞]]餐廳。<ref>{{cite web
 |title       = Melbourne Airport — General Facilities
 |publisher   = Melbourne Airport
 |url         = http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/airport_facilities/general.asp
 |accessdate  = 2008-09-27
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20080719185202/http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/airport_facilities/general.asp
 |archivedate = 2008-07-19
}}</ref>墨爾本機場高爾夫球會在北南跑旁。<ref>{{cite web
 |title       = Melbourne Airport — Golf Club
 |publisher   = Melbourne Airport
 |url         = http://www.melbourneairport.com.au/airport_facilities/golfclub.asp
 |accessdate  = 2008-09-27
